<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Immediately" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Immediately,</orth> 1) directly, expressly: <cit><quote>according to our law i. provided in that case,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 45</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>and apprehended here i. the unknown Ajax,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 124</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>for that offence i. we do exile him hence,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.192" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 192</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) instantly, without delay: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.6.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 6, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.2.64" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 2, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 5.250.64" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 250</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.287" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 287</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.156" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 156</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.5.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 5, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 9, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 9, 8</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.4.60" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 4, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.271" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 271</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.5.33" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.26" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 2, 26</bibl> (Ff <emph>presently</emph>). <bibl n="shak. tit 5.1.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 1, 161</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 2, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 4.3.142" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. IV, 3, 142</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 5.1.15" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.271" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 271</bibl>.
